headline: Franklin Resources Gains 16% YTD as New Partnerships Spark Valuation Debate
summary: If you are puzzling over what to do with Franklin Resources stock right now, you are not alone. This is a name that often slips under the radar, but recent moves are putting it firmly in the spotlight for investors looking for value and stability. Having climbed 3.2% over the past week and up an impressive 16.1% year-to-date, Franklin Resources is proving it still has runway, even as broader markets shift and reprice risk. Behind these moves, there have also been some headlines worth noting...
